<li>Make the most of the summer quiet. Book a session with us in <a href="https://localiq.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener">August</a>, and enjoy a 10% discount. #BookToday #[IndustrySpecificHashtag]</li>
<li>We sweat your success. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f605.png" alt="üòÖ" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></li>
</ul>
<h2>Try seasonal summer Instagram captions to brighten up your page</h2>
<p>Regardless of your industry or target audience, seasonal messaging can help reinvigorate your copy and recapture your followers‚Äô attention. This summer, try sprinkling in some seasonal posts alongside your regular ones (and try some of these <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/summer-puns">summer puns</a>!). You just might notice that readers are extra excited to see content that aligns with the vibes of the season. If you&#8217;re really crafty, you can get your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/instagram-posts-indexed-on-google">Instagram posts to show up in Google Search</a>.</p>
