<li>Cinco de Mayo ‚Äì every May 5</li>
<li>Teacher Appreciation Day ‚Äì Tuesday of the first full week in May</li>
<li>Mother‚Äôs Day ‚Äì May 11</li>
<li>Limerick Day ‚Äì every May 12</li>
<li>Peace Officer‚Äôs Memorial Day ‚Äì May 15</li>
