<h3>Peace Officer‚Äôs Memorial Day</h3>
<p>As a part of Public Service Recognition Week, we have Peace Officer‚Äôs Memorial Day on May 15. In addition to our troops and veterans, no one deserves our admiration more than those who serve and protect our cities. Take a moment to give a big thank you to your town‚Äôs protectors and even offer up specials specifically for Peace Officers.</p>
